1
00:01:31,100 --> 00:01:34,980
=Wonder Wall=

2
00:01:35,020 --> 00:01:37,910
=Episode 18=

3
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:54,959
Found it.

4
00:01:57,840 --> 00:01:58,359
Evidence bag.

5
00:01:58,439 --> 00:01:58,879
Got it.

6
00:01:59,519 --> 00:02:00,519
Go check for any cameras.

7
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:12,960
These are all old alleys.

8
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:13,800
No cameras.

9
00:02:23,319 --> 00:02:23,960
Now, we have one.

10
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:26,919
Captain Guo.

11
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:28,039
The suspect is not on site.

12
00:02:28,159 --> 00:02:29,319
The phone was left in the trash can.

13
00:02:29,639 --> 00:02:30,439
But there's a camera here.

14
00:02:30,639 --> 00:02:31,479
It should have filmed everything.

15
00:02:45,479 --> 00:02:45,919
Captain Guo.

16
00:02:46,080 --> 00:02:46,680
Yu Ming parked the Jinbei van

17
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:47,319
by the road.

18
00:02:48,159 --> 00:02:49,240
He's waiting for the kidnapper's call.

19
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:50,039
Keep a close watch.

20
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:50,680
Yes.

21
00:02:56,719 --> 00:02:57,240
Get out.

22
00:03:19,591 --> 00:03:20,039
(Match)

23
00:03:20,039 --> 00:03:20,560
(Match)
Captain Guo.

24
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:21,599
The matching results are in.

25
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:22,800
Zhan Chun lost the phone

26
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:23,360
on Gaoshi Street.

27
00:03:23,919 --> 00:03:24,520
Where is he now?

28
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:25,439
He went into Jiujing Street.

29
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:26,080
The fork is easy to spot.

30
00:03:26,319 --> 00:03:27,000
Two roads have cameras.

31
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:27,759
Rewind, and we'll locate him.

32
00:03:28,159 --> 00:03:29,400
But the roundabout
has four or five turnoffs

33
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:30,240
and no cameras. Hard to find him.

34
00:03:31,439 --> 00:03:32,039
Found it.

35
00:03:32,199 --> 00:03:33,240
We found his motorcycle.

36
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:34,039
Where did he go?

37
00:03:34,159 --> 00:03:34,960
Headed toward Binjia Town.

38
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:36,400
Contact Binjia Town.

39
00:03:36,599 --> 00:03:37,840
Comb every street, one by one.

40
00:03:54,479 --> 00:03:55,599
He entered Binjia Town and headed west.

41
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:57,199
Now he's in a camera blind spot.

42
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:58,319
That is an industrial zone.

43
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:59,840
There are many abandoned factories
and warehouses.

44
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:01,039
Set up a checkpoint
in the southern area.

45
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:02,479
Launch a grid search.

46
00:04:02,719 --> 00:04:03,319
We must find him

47
00:04:03,319 --> 00:04:04,439
before he reaches the hostage.

48
00:04:04,719 --> 00:04:05,360
Yes.

49
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:09,159
Let me tell you about domestic violence.

50
00:04:09,199 --> 00:04:11,000
It's never just once.

51
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:13,120
If he ever beats you again,

52
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:14,639
what will you do?

53
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:16,600
If it really comes down to it,

54
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:18,480
I'll stay at my relative's place
in Binjia Town.

55
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:20,000
I can hide in their scrapyard.

56
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:21,800
Guo Li.

57
00:04:23,879 --> 00:04:24,600
What's wrong, Yitong?

58
00:04:27,319 --> 00:04:28,639
I just remembered something.

59
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:30,480
Jiang Juan mentioned before

60
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:31,519
that she has a relative

61
00:04:32,079 --> 00:04:33,639
at a scrapyard in Binjia Town.

62
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:35,120
This is a key clue.

63
00:04:35,160 --> 00:04:35,879
We'll look into it.

64
00:04:36,199 --> 00:04:37,079
Don't worry, Yitong.

65
00:04:37,079 --> 00:04:38,079
Okay, okay.

66
00:04:39,199 --> 00:04:40,319
Relax, take it easy.

67
00:04:41,399 --> 00:04:42,160
The police will handle it.

68
00:04:42,759 --> 00:04:43,439
They'll find her.

69
00:05:07,079 --> 00:05:07,759
Give me the money.

70
00:05:09,759 --> 00:05:10,439
Or I'll give this

71
00:05:10,439 --> 00:05:11,160
to the police.

72
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:12,720
You know what's inside.

73
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:14,040
Du Lei gave you that?

74
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:17,680
Du Lei is Chen Liyang's eyes.

75
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:20,160
He watched me go to prison

76
00:05:20,839 --> 00:05:21,959
and watched me get out.

77
00:05:22,839 --> 00:05:24,160
He watched over my apartment,

78
00:05:25,199 --> 00:05:27,279
how many cups of coffee
I drink every day,

79
00:05:27,319 --> 00:05:28,439
what kind of wine I drink

80
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:30,240
what time I go to sleep,

81
00:05:30,279 --> 00:05:31,399
even who I meet.

82
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:34,399
It's annoying.

83
00:05:37,319 --> 00:05:38,439
That just means you feel guilty.

84
00:05:39,199 --> 00:05:40,120
Have some decency.

85
00:05:41,199 --> 00:05:42,279
Don't burn all your bridges.

86
00:05:43,839 --> 00:05:45,120
Even if it's a dead end, I'll take it.

87
00:05:50,639 --> 00:05:52,040
Then you'll just have to
walk into prison

88
00:05:52,199 --> 00:05:52,959
and keep saying "reporting in."

89
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:54,639
I sent you in once.

90
00:05:56,360 --> 00:05:57,279
I can do it again.

91
00:05:59,439 --> 00:06:00,360
Once, twice.

92
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:05,040
So what?

93
00:06:08,199 --> 00:06:09,399
Even if you wanted my life,

94
00:06:12,519 --> 00:06:13,319
I'd give it to you.

95
00:06:15,199 --> 00:06:16,319
Because you are my daughter.

96
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:23,199
Now, you have the USB drive.

97
00:06:23,959 --> 00:06:24,639
My life

98
00:06:25,199 --> 00:06:25,959
is your call.

99
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,519
Those years in prison,

100
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:31,000
every time

101
00:06:31,399 --> 00:06:32,639
family visitation came around,

102
00:06:33,279 --> 00:06:33,920
the night before,

103
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:35,519
I was too excited to fall asleep.

104
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:39,160
I was hoping

105
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:41,519
to see you.

106
00:06:43,199 --> 00:06:43,920
Five years.

107
00:06:44,879 --> 00:06:46,360
You never came to see me.

108
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,519
Not once.

109
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:54,319
After I got out,

110
00:06:57,279 --> 00:06:58,600
I could only drink, nonstop.

111
00:06:59,319 --> 00:07:00,240
I drink every single day.

112
00:07:00,959 --> 00:07:02,600
Only when I was numb with drink,

113
00:07:03,319 --> 00:07:04,240
in my dreams,

114
00:07:08,439 --> 00:07:09,120
could I see

115
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:10,519
you smiling at me,

116
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:13,319
could I see your face clearly.

117
00:07:15,879 --> 00:07:16,480
Nuo,

118
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:17,720
I'm your mother,

119
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:19,439
and I only want you to be happy.

120
00:07:22,959 --> 00:07:23,600
Where is the money?

121
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:28,879
It's in the garage.

122
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,879
Do whatever you want with it.

123
00:07:36,279 --> 00:07:37,439
Today is my birthday.

124
00:07:41,160 --> 00:07:42,519
Would you have a drink with me?

125
00:08:25,279 --> 00:08:26,160
Happy birthday.

126
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:02,559
Happy birthday.

127
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:16,799
Can you go faster, please?

128
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:18,000
Any faster and we'll be speeding.

129
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:00,600
Zoom in on this and let me see.

130
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:03,720
Captain Guo.

131
00:10:04,679 --> 00:10:05,399
This is Chief Xiang

132
00:10:05,399 --> 00:10:06,279
from the Binjia police station.

133
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:07,399
- Hello, Chief Xiang.
- Captain Guo.

134
00:10:08,639 --> 00:10:09,639
I've reviewed the footage.

135
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:11,159
The road he took

136
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:12,200
gets more deserted as it heads west.

137
00:10:12,519 --> 00:10:13,519
Ahead, there are two villages,

138
00:10:13,559 --> 00:10:14,639
but they've been completely demolished.

139
00:10:15,039 --> 00:10:15,799
The only possible hiding place

140
00:10:15,799 --> 00:10:16,480
is a scrapyard.

141
00:10:16,559 --> 00:10:17,840
We call it the "car graveyard" here.

142
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,480
To the right is a forested area.

143
00:10:19,679 --> 00:10:20,679
Go past the forest,

144
00:10:20,960 --> 00:10:21,960
and you will see an old railway.

145
00:10:37,679 --> 00:10:38,080
Captain.

146
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,200
The kidnapper's phone.

147
00:10:39,759 --> 00:10:40,360
Everyone, be quiet.

148
00:10:40,639 --> 00:10:41,440
Pick it up. On speaker.

149
00:10:44,600 --> 00:10:45,120
Listen to me.

150
00:10:45,159 --> 00:10:46,440
I... I saw

151
00:10:46,759 --> 00:10:47,799
that black case you gave me.

152
00:10:47,799 --> 00:10:48,320
I opened it.

153
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:49,159
You achieved your goal.

154
00:10:49,159 --> 00:10:49,919
I'm really scared.

155
00:10:49,919 --> 00:10:50,919
Trust me, I didn't call the police.

156
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:52,919
As for me taking the van,
it's because...

157
00:10:52,919 --> 00:10:53,559
Yu Ming!

158
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:54,600
Now what?

159
00:10:55,919 --> 00:10:56,519
Bigfoot?

160
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:58,039
How did you get

161
00:10:58,039 --> 00:10:58,960
the kidnapper's phone?

162
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:00,320
You caught him?

163
00:11:00,559 --> 00:11:01,200
Hang it up!

164
00:11:24,679 --> 00:11:25,440
It'll be fine.

165
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:27,600
Xiao,

166
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:28,919
the kidnapper is already contained

167
00:11:28,919 --> 00:11:29,360
in Binjia Town.

168
00:11:29,480 --> 00:11:30,399
Pull your team back now

169
00:11:30,440 --> 00:11:31,039
to assist with the arrest.

170
00:11:31,279 --> 00:11:31,759
Yes.

171
00:11:32,080 --> 00:11:32,879
Everyone into the vehicles.

172
00:11:32,960 --> 00:11:33,679
Back to the command center.

173
00:11:33,759 --> 00:11:34,440
Everyone into the vehicles.

174
00:12:07,914 --> 00:12:08,828
(This folder is empty)

175
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:36,879
Du lei,

176
00:12:38,519 --> 00:12:39,360
you've crossed the line.

177
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:42,399
You can stick your nose in some things,

178
00:12:43,840 --> 00:12:44,559
but other things,

179
00:12:45,960 --> 00:12:46,879
you shouldn't meddle with.

180
00:12:47,480 --> 00:12:49,000
Anything that concerns Zinuo,

181
00:12:49,759 --> 00:12:50,759
I have to get involved.

182
00:12:57,679 --> 00:12:59,519
Zinuo dared to come
with an empty USB drive

183
00:12:59,519 --> 00:13:00,320
and deceive me

184
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:03,559
just because you told her

185
00:13:03,639 --> 00:13:04,759
that you had a backup, right?

186
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:08,879
You ruined her.

187
00:13:09,600 --> 00:13:10,840
She is your daughter.

188
00:13:11,879 --> 00:13:13,320
You don't deserve to be a mother.

189
00:13:19,039 --> 00:13:20,840
Chen Liyang spared your life back then,

190
00:13:21,399 --> 00:13:23,120
and this is how you treat me?

191
00:13:23,960 --> 00:13:25,519
Mr. Chen spared my life

192
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:27,320
to take care of Zinuo.

193
00:13:32,960 --> 00:13:33,480
Zinuo.

194
00:13:34,799 --> 00:13:35,320
Zinuo.

195
00:13:37,240 --> 00:13:38,879
Don't you have something to give me?

196
00:13:42,879 --> 00:13:44,600
The money and the USB drive are hers.

197
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:46,159
None of your business.

198
00:13:49,320 --> 00:13:50,360
Sun Leping.

199
00:13:55,360 --> 00:13:56,399
It's been a long time since anyone

200
00:13:56,399 --> 00:13:57,559
called you by that name, hasn't it?

201
00:13:59,679 --> 00:14:00,600
You think that after all these years,

202
00:14:00,600 --> 00:14:01,799
changing your identity

203
00:14:02,279 --> 00:14:03,440
can erase your past?

204
00:14:11,799 --> 00:14:13,000
I can turn myself in,

205
00:14:13,879 --> 00:14:15,039
but you can't get away.

206
00:15:07,600 --> 00:15:09,000
Only when you're dead

207
00:15:09,279 --> 00:15:10,799
can I be completely clean.

208
00:15:19,120 --> 00:15:19,799
Lei.

209
00:15:22,960 --> 00:15:23,919
What do you want?

210
00:15:25,720 --> 00:15:27,279
I spent five years in prison.

211
00:15:29,200 --> 00:15:30,840
I paid my debt a long time ago.

212
00:15:31,159 --> 00:15:32,879
Why are you still pushing me?

213
00:15:33,600 --> 00:15:34,279
So...

214
00:15:34,799 --> 00:15:36,120
So you have to die.

215
00:15:36,320 --> 00:15:36,919
No.

216
00:15:37,399 --> 00:15:38,519
This is murder.

217
00:15:38,720 --> 00:15:39,840
You're killing!

218
00:15:39,919 --> 00:15:41,480
Do you realize what you're doing?

219
00:15:41,519 --> 00:15:42,960
They pushed me to this!

220
00:15:43,480 --> 00:15:44,480
What did I do?

221
00:15:44,919 --> 00:15:45,559
Do you know

222
00:15:45,559 --> 00:15:46,559
what he backed up

223
00:15:46,879 --> 00:15:47,840
means I'll never see you again

224
00:15:47,840 --> 00:15:49,080
for the rest of my life?

225
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:49,799
Everything I've done

226
00:15:49,799 --> 00:15:50,679
is for you!

227
00:15:50,679 --> 00:15:52,120
Get out of the way. He must die.

228
00:15:53,720 --> 00:15:55,240
You're the murderer.

229
00:15:59,200 --> 00:15:59,639
You...

230
00:16:03,639 --> 00:16:04,320
Nuo,

231
00:16:05,639 --> 00:16:07,080
you're pointing a knife at me.

232
00:16:07,559 --> 00:16:08,440
In your heart,

233
00:16:09,720 --> 00:16:11,159
I always come second to an outsider.

234
00:16:11,159 --> 00:16:11,759
Is that it?

235
00:16:12,200 --> 00:16:13,879
What am I to you, inside your heart?

236
00:16:14,039 --> 00:16:14,919
Everything I did

237
00:16:14,919 --> 00:16:15,919
was for you!

238
00:16:15,960 --> 00:16:17,399
You don't know. You don't understand!

239
00:16:17,399 --> 00:16:18,279
Everything I've done,

240
00:16:18,279 --> 00:16:19,919
I just wanted to go back
to how things were.

241
00:16:19,960 --> 00:16:21,600
I wanted you to come back to me.

242
00:16:22,759 --> 00:16:23,600
You can't go back.

243
00:16:25,159 --> 00:16:26,080
You can't.

244
00:16:31,720 --> 00:16:32,279
Lei!

245
00:16:32,919 --> 00:16:33,480
Lei!

246
00:16:43,639 --> 00:16:44,360
Lei!

247
00:16:45,919 --> 00:16:47,639
It's already gotten out of hand.

248
00:16:48,639 --> 00:16:50,399
(2018)
Neither Li Jin nor I can get away.

249
00:16:52,600 --> 00:16:54,080
(2018)
I can't stop worrying about Zinuo.

250
00:16:55,279 --> 00:16:56,159
I'll take the fall for this.

251
00:16:59,519 --> 00:17:01,679
Li Jin will be out in a few years.

252
00:17:02,240 --> 00:17:04,000
She loses control easily.

253
00:17:05,599 --> 00:17:06,480
After she gets out, if she

254
00:17:06,519 --> 00:17:07,839
treats Zinuo well,

255
00:17:08,519 --> 00:17:09,480
then you serve her.

256
00:17:10,400 --> 00:17:12,160
Whatever you do for me, you do for her.

257
00:17:13,880 --> 00:17:15,400
But if she tries to control

258
00:17:15,400 --> 00:17:16,680
or hurt Zinuo,

259
00:17:17,559 --> 00:17:18,200
take her out.

260
00:17:19,279 --> 00:17:20,200
I won't be able to

261
00:17:20,240 --> 00:17:21,440
watch over Zinuo anymore.

262
00:17:21,559 --> 00:17:23,000
You need to be my eyes.

263
00:17:25,079 --> 00:17:25,440
Leave, now.

264
00:17:30,160 --> 00:17:30,720
Lei.

265
00:17:30,960 --> 00:17:32,160
Only when he's dead

266
00:17:32,799 --> 00:17:34,000
will we have peace.

267
00:17:35,440 --> 00:17:37,079
You're the one who destroys all peace!

268
00:17:37,119 --> 00:17:38,880
You destroy everyone's peace!

269
00:17:39,559 --> 00:17:40,960
You're the devil!

270
00:17:41,160 --> 00:17:42,160
You're a demon!

271
00:17:51,559 --> 00:17:52,119
Nuo.

272
00:18:03,845 --> 00:18:05,405
(Bridgeway Financial)

273
00:18:06,200 --> 00:18:06,839
Zinuo!

274
00:18:08,359 --> 00:18:08,960
Zinuo!

275
00:19:01,279 --> 00:19:02,160
How did you discover

276
00:19:02,160 --> 00:19:02,960
this case?

277
00:19:05,599 --> 00:19:06,839
I came for my friend.

278
00:19:08,759 --> 00:19:09,559
After I went in,

279
00:19:10,880 --> 00:19:12,359
I found someone lying on the ground.

280
00:19:16,160 --> 00:19:17,279
I know who the murderer is.

281
00:19:19,240 --> 00:19:19,799
It's Li Jin.

282
00:19:21,960 --> 00:19:22,599
Steady.

283
00:19:23,119 --> 00:19:23,799
Be careful.

284
00:19:23,799 --> 00:19:25,039
Run! Run!

285
00:19:25,400 --> 00:19:26,480
Grandma, I'm scared.

286
00:19:26,640 --> 00:19:27,799
Don't be afraid. Run!

287
00:19:27,799 --> 00:19:29,559
Run out and get someone to save me.

288
00:19:31,839 --> 00:19:32,720
Running again? Get down here.

289
00:19:32,720 --> 00:19:33,240
Grandma!

290
00:19:34,039 --> 00:19:34,759
